living according to his principles gene siskel in the chicago 
tribune 
</TEXT>
<TEXT>
the last temptation of christ is as powerful as it is 
controversial a work of passion and imagination that stirs the 
soul and shakes the intellect lloyd sachs of the chicago 
suntimes 
