with 3112 percent and clouthier trailed with 1707 percent 
as for the pridominated election complaint tribunal it has 
rejected about 90 percent of nearly 600 fraud charges 
the outcome of the electoral college session may be virtually 
certain but it wont perform what was once a mere formality 
without public notice 
