expected about the end of the year 
present kash n karry employees would keep their jobs under the 
proposed acquisition by a managementallied group including ron 
floto president and chief executive officer kash n karry with 
headquarters in tampa has 95 supermarkets in central and western 
florida 
financing for the management buyout is being arranged by 
gibbons green van amerogen which has financed many such 
management buyouts the partnership said in a news release 
american acquired lucky in a leveraged buyout meaning the 
purchase was financed by loans assets of the acquired company 
often are sold off to pay the debt from such purchases but 
american spokesman troy dambrosio declined to say if more sales 
were pending 
